    "name": "FBurger API",
    "description": "Backend API for FBurger - A burger restaurant application with authentication, products, reviews, users management, and dashboard statistics.\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require JWT authentication via Bearer token in the Authorization header.\n\n## Base URL\nUse the `{{baseUrl}}` variable (default: http://localhost:3000/api)\n\n## Roles\n- **admin**: Full access to all endpoints\n- **user**: Can view products and create reviews\n- **visitor**: Can view products and create account",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
